name: Diving into the Unknown
description:
This artwork is about diving into life to find deepest conscience that is almost drowned in the ocean, and almost fully consumed by the darkness itself. the conscience is metaphorized as a pearl (a symbol of purity), and the octopus symbolizes the darkest shadow of ourselves.
to conquer the darkest self , we have to transform into something that can be accepted. (transforming birds into sea creatures too)
